  <text x="330" y="122" fill="#71717a" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="13">7/15 $64,977 → 7/16 $64,055 → 7/17 $63,394</text>
  <text x="20" y="170" fill="#d4d4d8" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14" font-weight="700">Macro Leg — The Pressing Side</text>
  <rect x="20" y="182" width="660" height="92" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#3f3f46"/>
  <text x="40" y="208" fill="#f87171" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="17" font-weight="800">10-Year Yield 4.57-4.58% (Rebounding)</text>
