  <text x="35" y="370" fill="#34d399" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="22" font-weight="800">36 (Fear)</text>
  <text x="35" y="396" fill="#71717a" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="12">Up from 21 (Extreme Fear) on 7/3</text>
